description:
ANN Weekly highlights several stories from locations around the globe.

This week, learn how the Church in the Inter-European region is planning for mission in 2023 despite the challenges they face in their context.

Discover how access to Adventist education is opening opportunities for women in Mongolia.

Find these stories and more on our website, adventist.news.
